title: CDDIS_GNSS_products_ionosphere_rapid
summary: Ionosphere Total Electron Content (TEC) grids derived from analysis of Global Navigation Satellite System (GNSS) data. These products are the generated by analysis centers in support of the International GNSS Service (IGS) and combined by the IGS ionosphere analysis coordinator to form the official IGS rapid ionosphere product (daily).
